Design Document

mage Interfaces
Operations : castAttackSpell(String spellName, Character target)
             castDefenseSpell(String spellName)

Sorcerer
Operations : castSpellTwice(String spellName, Character target)

Druid
Operations : castNaturalPower(String naturalElement, Character target)

Necromancer
Operations : summonSpirit(String spiritName)
             spiritAttack(String spiritName,Character target)

-------------------------------------------------------------------

magicItem Interfaces
Operations : upMagicStat(int spellPower, int mana)

bookOfSpell
Operations :  upgradeSpell(String spellName)

magicWand
Operations : castSpecialDefenseSpell(String specialSpellName)
             castSpecialAttackSpell(String specialSpellName, Character target)

skullCrystal
Operations : cancelEnemyAttack()




